  "description": "The optimization modpack of the Cobblemon mod, for Fabric!",
  "body": "<p></p><center><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p5FdgNy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"660\"></center><p></p>\n\n<p></p><center><span><font size=\"5\"><strong>Cobblefine is an Cobblemon optimization modpack for Fabric.</strong></font></span></center><p></p>\n\n<p></p><center><span><font size=\"4\"><em>The purpose of this modpack is to optimize the Cobblemon as much as possible on low-end computers and laptops, reduce stuttering, and increase FPS as much as possible.</em></font></span></center><p></p>\n\n<p></p><center><span><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MDU6h3W.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"838\" height=\"32\"></span></center><p></p>\n\n<p></p><center><span><font size=\"4\"><strong><em>Modpack Contents:</em></strong></font></span></center><p></p>\n\n<p></p><center><span><font size=\"4\"><em>This modpack will allow clients to connect to Fabric-based servers that only run Cobblemon.</em></font></span></center><p></p>\n\n<p></p><center><span><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MDU6h3W.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"838\" height=\"32\"></span></center><p></p>\n<p></p><center><span><font size=\"4\"><strong><em>Cobblefine is not an official modpack.</em></strong></font></span></center><p></p>\n<p></p><center><span><font size=\"4\"><em>This modpack was entirely created by fans.</em></font></span></center><p></p>",
